Ig3D Project : Second-Depth Shadow Mapping
Yona MELLUL, 3800646

Requirements: pygame, moderngl, PyGLM, pywavefront

To run the program: >> python main.py

To navigate the window:
- Use the four arrows to go up, down, right and left.
- Use the f key to go forward
- Use the b key to go backwords
- Use the mouse (or touchpad) to rotate
